text: Harringtonia dalmeidai is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Dillon and Dillon in 1946. It is known from Panama and Costa Rica.BioLib.cz - Harringtonia dalmeidai. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1946
